  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in the donabe over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and saut\u00138n until translucent.",
    "Add the grated ginger and saut\u00138n for another minute.",
    "Add the turmeric, salt, and black pepper. Stir to combine.",
    "Add the red rice and stir to coat with the spice mixture.",
    "Add the water to the donabe and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low, cover the donabe with a lid, and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "Uncover the donabe and fluff the rice with a fork.",
    "Serve hot garnished with chopped parsley, if desired."
